textBeforeTable: And now, ladies and gentlemen, we find ourselves at finals week. A bittersweet week yet Dissociative Identity will try to accompany you through these troubling times. Unfortunately I do not know yet what my new hours will be in 2014 however when I do, be sure to tune in either through that ancient beast known as the radio or online through WKDU Philadelphia, 91.7 fm. Our last show of the year includes BATS, Superchunk, Dungen, The Mamas and the Papas, in addition to the artisan poop you know you love. Pay close attention to Dissociative Identity Productions in order to learn about life and/or social networks. Defile the plural narrative? Maybe it's time. Cliff.DI Dissociative Identity on Tue 12/10/13
